reviewText:
My player(s) showed as follows  "Disc Error, Please eject this disc. Playback feature may not be available on this disc"

I have played hundred's of dvd's and cd's on these players and have never seen this message before.

not to worry, just one of those things.
Marc Anthony is amazing in this concert!!! His voice is clear and filled with passion. I will watch this over and over. Wish they would come out with a newer one!!
